Brian Van Holt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brian_Van_Holt 0 Brian Van Holt (born July 6, 1969) is an American actor. He is best known for playing Bo Sinclair in the ABC movie House Of Wax and Bobby Cobb on the TV series Cougar Town. Brian_Van_Holt ( born July_6_,_1969 ) is an_American_actor .
